The paper presents an approach to multi-task deep reinforcement learning, which involves machine learning, artificial intelligence, and robotics. The attention mechanism used in the approach is also relevant to computer vision. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.RO (Robotics). The approach also involves control systems (cs.SY) and computer vision (cs.CV), which are less likely but still relevant sub-categories.
